Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在橡树叶刚刚开始变红的秋天 我们前往格罗夫果园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And at the first blush of the oak leaves, we head to the Grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的麻烦是 从一地迁徙到另一地要历经重重危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only trouble is there's a hundred perils between here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是个危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的光 正在消逝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our light is fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘银…这是我们唯一的救赎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this mithril... It is our only salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以整个精灵族的命运…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the fate of the entire Elven race...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都掌握在你手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-...is in your hands. -Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索隆曾经是你们人类的敌人 也是我们精灵的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron was once your people's enemy as much as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求您重建 努门诺尔和精灵之间的联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I call on you to reforge the alliance between Númenor and Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救南方大地的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To save the men of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这下边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方大地真正的国王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指环王：力量之戒\N第一季第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃兰迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother? Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你受伤了吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you hurt? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安塔摩去哪了 刚才还和我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Ontamo? Ontamo was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬着走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬着走 我不会丢下你不管的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crawl. I won't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵 在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵 他咽气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他咽气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他咽气了… -快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's gone... -Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们救救我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Help! Please, help! -Soldiers! Over here! We're inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们 那个屋顶快要塌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That roof's about to come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快清出一条路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Can't get out! -Quickly, clear a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我的手 你不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take hold of my hand. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前走 别走散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go forward. Stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hurry, my Queen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往桥的方向走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go towards the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他们带离这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur! Isildur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老博尔格巴克去抓蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Bolgerbuck went snailing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金风玉露的秋日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One autumn day so fine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他找到了百只大蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He found a hundred big ones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望全都是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish that they were mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格罗夫 我觉得就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Grove! I think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话你三天前就已经说过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Said that three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 他说得对 我记得这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, he's right. I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到了吗 是柴火烟  其他毛脚肯定已经开始烘烤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you smell that? Wood smoke! The others must've started bakin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布罗斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾祖父以前 经常说起南方有些山能喷射岩浆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My great-grand used to speak of mountains to the south that could spit fire-rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说这些山会休眠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said they go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会长达数百年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在新的邪恶势力崛起时 它们才会再次喷发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only to wake again when a new evil is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白兰地足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那位朋友 那个大家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friend up there. The big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你不觉得… -觉得什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You don't suppose... -Suppose what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他能解决这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he could fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快去啊 诺瑞 -他之前还收拾了那群狼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Go on, Nori. -Yes. Like he fixed those wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在等什么  -我不知道…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Uh, I don't know... I don't know if he... -What you waitin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经为我们做了那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's done so much for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再对他提要求会显得我们有点无礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a mite rude of us to ask more of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll ask him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡道 小家伙们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out the way, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á keuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á envinyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Envinyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开花…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lót? na...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-开花… -他在嘀咕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lót? na... -What's he mutterin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计就是一些 很简单的词 好让大树能听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likely little words, so the tree'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨道克 树可不会说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc, trees don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些树是会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Envinyata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lót? na!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议 居然起作用了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great-goats. It's working...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á kuita! á kuita! á kuita!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在让大树起死回生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's fixin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如萨道克所说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like Sadoc said he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dilly, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No! -Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖女儿们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My sweet girls! My babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 迪莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Dilly! Dilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 诺瑞 你们没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dilly, Nori, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all right. I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们请求从这座大山获取神圣的矿石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ask for something sacred from this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作为回报 我们也会提供一些神圣的物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so we offer something sacred in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了换取你秘银矿的使用权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In exchange for access to your mithril mines,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵族准备 连续五个世纪为这座城市供应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Elves are prepared to furnish this city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家具 动物 谷物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with game, grain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及来自埃利阿多古老森林的木材\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and timber from the elder forests of Eriador for the next five centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们说话算数 那这个承诺可不一般…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite a promise, if they can keep it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向来信守承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never made a promise I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经学会了几个石语的词汇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see you've learned a few words of stone-tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 我们为什么要相信精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, why should we trust any Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不应该相信精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不是普通的精灵 我可是埃尔隆德半精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For I am no common Elf, but Elrond Half-elven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在精灵身上看到了 他们在自己身上看不到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I see in Elves that which they cannot see in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在孤身求见…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I stand before you now, alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恳求您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you to save my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊贵的国王 请帮帮我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, noble King. Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和我儿子说两句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will speak to my son now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您准备怎么答复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is to be your answer, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说当年奥力创造我们矮人时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is said that when Aul? created our people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用到了两种元素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he crafted us of two elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火与石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire and rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们体内的石元素渴望永恒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rock that lives within us hungers for the eternal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗拒时间的拉扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}resisting the pull of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而火元素拥抱真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the fire embraces truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信万物总有一天都会消耗殆尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That all things must one day be consumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-然后化作灰尘 -父亲…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-...and fade away to ash... -Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从不挖掘容易塌陷的大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not dig in earth that cannot support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也从不钻入黑暗之外的深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Delving into depths beyond the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不会冒上被 阴影 岩石和矿场埋葬山底的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tempting shadow, rock, and mine to bury us all beneath the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会拿矮人们的生命冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not risk Dwarven lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去帮助精灵逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to help the Elves cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cheat death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友身处险境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friend is drowning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在伸手向我求援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}reaching for me to pull him to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就因为害怕石头坠落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You expect me to swat his hand away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我甩开他的手坐视不管吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you're afraid of a bloody rock fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵族的命运 早在几个纪元之前就已经被决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fate of the Elves was decided many Ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些决定者远比我们更具智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By minds much wiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们更有远见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}much farther-seeing than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如若违抗他们的意志 那我们整个王国都可能会崩塌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Defy their will, and this entire kingdom might fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至整个中洲都会如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps the entire Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但精灵族的命数已尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But their time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟老头子 冷漠 愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lice-bearded, uncaring, old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他说得对呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会坐视不管吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not thinking of lettin' this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有别的选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过其他矮人领主 对这项提议持开放态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said the other Dwarf-lords were open to the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们自己重新开矿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we reopen the mine ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向其他领主证明 可以有安全的方法开采秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}prove to them there's a safe way to gather mithril,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能让你父亲听进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}perhaps they'd make him listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们可以强迫你父亲出手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we could force your father's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不光是我的父亲啊 迪莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's more than just my father, Disa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是我们的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's our king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我教给孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of father would I be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王的意志可以当做耳旁风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I teach our children the will of a king
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我还算哪门子父亲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should be counted as dross to be cast to the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才不应该说他是个糟老头子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have said he had lice in his beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也不该骂他愚蠢 -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Or called him a fool. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就是讨厌 你对我母亲的各种讽刺批评\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I detest it when you heap slag on my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲确实是有点糟糕…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, well, in your mother's case, she actually does have lice in her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm joking. I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我不能强留你吃晚饭了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't suppose I can elbow you into staying for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得向吉尔加拉德报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gil-galad must be informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快他将不再是国王 因为林顿很快将不复存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And soon, he will no longer be a king, for there will no longer be a Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这就是道别了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So this is goodbye, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从不道别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do not say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们会说Namá… -Namári?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We say namá... -Namári?.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含义远比单纯的“告别”更丰富\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means more than simply "farewell."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是：“愿你向善而行”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means... "Go towards goodness."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们为什么要这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd they do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把这里变成它们的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make this their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的魔影之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their Shadow Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就把土地夺回来 把它们赶走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we take it back, and drive them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们位置不利 也没有增援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have neither position, nor reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These lands are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须把活着的人集结起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must rally to the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者将敌人一剑封喉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or put steel down their throats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言没有结束 我也不允许结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me. I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须停手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在苦恼什么 这又不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you so bothered about? It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进 就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep moving. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮后边的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help those people at the back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-女王  -她还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The Queen! -She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-女王 -她来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is she hurt? -Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她没事吧  -我还以为我们痛失女王了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is she hurt? -Is she all right? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请骑我的马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-船长… -他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Captain... -Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是战死了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're dead, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆迪尔 我的朋友们 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arondir. My friends. My...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲 所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的事情 会严重影响思绪 我们不能胡乱猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What cannot be known hollows the mind. Fill it not with guesswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we even going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努门诺尔在那条山脊线上安营扎寨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Númenor set their camp upon that ridgeline,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那个远处的山峰后边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beyond that far peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该和其他幸存者都跑去了那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is where they shall hie to, along with any survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mother included.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高警惕 奥克现在白天也会出来行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And be wary. The Orcs will move in daylight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前杀过奥克 你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've killed Orcs before, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像你这个年纪的时候 根本没有奥克这种东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was your age, there was no such thing as Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在呢 你杀过多少奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now? How many have you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很多 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Many. -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会用“很好”这样的词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would not use such words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黑暗的杀戮行径称为“很好” 会让内心变得黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It darkens the heart, to call dark deeds "good."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗会乘虚而入在我们体内滋长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It gives place for evil to thrive inside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每场战争都有外在之仗和内在之仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every war is fought both without and within.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此 所有士兵都必须谨慎留意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of that, every soldier must be mindful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你我也不例外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even I. Even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算士兵了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I a soldier, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们可以把你算作士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we can make one of you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要走多远才能到达营地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much further until we reach the encampment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这个坡就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just beyond this rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.33,0:24:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要走多远眼前的烟雾才能散去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much further until we're clear of this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.58,0:25:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾已经散去多远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long have we been clear of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将近一英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nearly a mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能看清楚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.20,0:25:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看到灰蒙蒙的一片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep walking, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.91,0:25:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵着我的马 别让任何人看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guide my horse. No one need notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃兰迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃兰迪尔 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.29,0:25:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们称这里为大绿林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call it Greenwood the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.29,0:26:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把头低下 眼睛盯紧那片悬崖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your head down and your eye on that line of cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.87,0:26:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会在远处找到人类的居住地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll find the big folk settlements on the far side.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的话 那里的人可以帮你找到你的星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With any luck, the people there can help you find your stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只能告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause all I can tell you is,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打一千多年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoot-folk haven't seen 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祖先生活在不知名的地方以来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since the days our ancestors lived in parts unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.37,0:26:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛脚族就没见过他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便对你这种大长腿而言 走这么遥远的路也绝非易事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's a long time to wander. Even for a fellow with big legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不应该偏离路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should've just stayed on-trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.33,0:29:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道当初看到 那颗坠落的星星时 我就该放任不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I saw that star falling, I should've just let it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-埃拉诺… -您之前提醒过我 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elanor... -You tried to tell me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在才明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个毛脚族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just a Harfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.25,0:29:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远只会是个毛脚族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.20,0:29:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去睡觉吧 诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off to bed, Nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.58,0:29:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事我们可以早上再处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can tend to the rest in the mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去过亲近的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever lost someone close?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被奥克杀害的那种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说亲戚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.75,0:30:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥 芬罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother. Finrod.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.41,0:30:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.25,0:30:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.54,0:30:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫凯勒博恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celeborn was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.04,0:30:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们初识于一片花丛中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We met in a glade of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.75,0:30:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我在跳舞 他看到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was dancing and he saw me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 跳舞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.95,0:31:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候战争似乎还很遥远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The war seemed so very far away then.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去参战的时候 我还责备了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he went to it, I chided him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的盔甲不合身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His armor didn't fit properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.79,0:31:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就嘲笑他像个银蛤蜊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I called him a silver clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.87,0:31:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之后我再也没有见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never saw him again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.04,0:31:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前所说的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.66,0:31:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不正确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.25,0:31:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样也并非你的本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did not intend for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.12,0:31:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给了敌人力量 所以我有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave power to the enemy. So that makes me responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.29,0:31:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说 世间万物就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some say that is the way of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信聪明的人 还会审视我们的初衷和本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I believe the wise also look upon what is in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.70,0:32:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样绝非你的本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this was not in yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.95,0:32:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把今天的重担都揽在 自己肩上 希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not take the burden of this day upon your shoulders, Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.79,0:32:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会发现 重担一旦扛起 想要卸下就会很难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may find it difficult to put it down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.25,0:32:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我怎么才能做到放手呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how am I to let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上 有超越黑暗的力量在运作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are powers beyond darkness at work in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许在这样的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps on days such as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们别无选择 只能相信他们的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've little choice but to trust to their designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.66,0:32:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃我们自己的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And surrender our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.75,0:32:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My home is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.37,0:32:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里边有什么计划可言吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the design in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还看不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot yet see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.08,0:33:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.62,0:33:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 你闻到了什么味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? What do you smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.79,0:34:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.87,0:34:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有 只有灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' but ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.83,0:34:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我们这是在浪费时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. We're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.54,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能多休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rest while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.62,0:34:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天一亮我们就出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We move at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.37,0:34:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪还有天亮可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What light?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一波震动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.04,0:35:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得先等岩石稳定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to give the rocks time to resettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵大师 要高度自律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Self-discipline, master Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自律能给你带来成功吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think that'll bring you success?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正让我在比赛中赢了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It did in our contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.66,0:35:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意输给我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lost on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.66,0:36:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标从来都不是打败你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My aim was never to defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.00,0:36:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是得到你的持续关注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to gain your ear a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.29,0:36:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这精灵撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.91,0:36:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时就是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.54,0:36:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累得没喘上气而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.87,0:36:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.66,0:36:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得 你这精灵身上有点矮人的特质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always thought you were a mite Dwarvish for an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我觉得 你是个有精灵特征的矮人 都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are a rather Elvish Dwarf, Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.04,0:36:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林之子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Son of Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那谁…的孙子 -随便你怎么嘲笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Grandson of... -Scoff if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.45,0:37:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人最伟大的成就 就是不负父辈的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mightiest thing a Dwarf can do is to be worthy of the name of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.54,0:37:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们确实有自己的秘密名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do have our secret names,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.20,0:37:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只供自己人使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for use only amongst ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.95,0:37:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些名字只会告诉家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we reveal them only to family.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子 父母 姐妹 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wives, parents, sisters, brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.08,0:37:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-埃尔隆德… -先别说了 都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elrond... -Save it, Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.79,0:37:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成功了再告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the far side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.66,0:37:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.54,0:39:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.45,0:39:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.54,0:39:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘银比我们想象的还要多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's more than we ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都林国王 有一个… -够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-King Durin, there is a... -Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.83,0:39:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, just look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那个精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seize the Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初你母亲生你的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When your mother bore you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.16,0:40:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你体内是有某种缺陷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something inside you was ill-formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼吸又干又涩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your breathing was ragged and dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸声很微弱 很可怜 就像白堊石在刮擦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A tiny, pitiful sound, like scraping chalkstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们说你肯定熬不过第一个冬天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Folk said you'd never see your first winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.83,0:40:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲哭累了入睡之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after your mother's weeping eyes had found refuge in sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.37,0:41:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会把你抱到火光下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I held you to the firelight,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.62,0:41:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚都抬着你的下巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kept your chin up all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.66,0:41:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样似乎减轻了一点负担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seemed to ease the burden a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one night,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凝视着你乳臭未干的小脸蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gazed down on your tiny, naked face,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.58,0:41:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛从中看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I saw upon it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.87,0:41:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位老矮人国王的白色胡须\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the great gray beard of an old Dwarven-king.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.20,0:41:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像奔赴战场的军队一样强大而霸气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mighty and terrible as an army with banners.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.29,0:41:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你母亲醒来时我告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when your mother woke, I told her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.54,0:41:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以后不用再哭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she need cry no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.41,0:41:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的儿子会活着 会有移山填海般的出息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our son would live and he would move mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.87,0:42:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我挖个小洞您就能气成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you expect me to move mountains, Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还指望我如何移山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you fall to pieces when I dig a single hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.41,0:42:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您嘴上说着让我立下辉煌大业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak of greatness for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.33,0:42:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却扼杀我的所有野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you suffocate in me any ambition,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.29,0:42:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有渴望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.33,0:42:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及任何只要不是源自于您的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any thought that does not originate in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.54,0:42:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天将降大任于斯人也\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The iron that must bear the most heavy of burdens
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.91,0:42:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必先苦其心志 劳其筋骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}must also endure the most rigorous tempering!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.33,0:42:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让盟友去送死可不是苦心志劳筋骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consigning your allies to death is not tempering.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.75,0:42:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德和我情同手足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond is as much a brother to me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是同一个母亲生的亲兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as if he'd been fired in my own mother's womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.16,0:42:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么敢…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.66,0:42:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没大没小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.08,0:42:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你母亲的记忆说事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Invoke your mother's memory
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.79,0:42:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此来为背叛同胞的决定狡辩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to defend your decision to betray your own kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.50,0:43:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你背叛了我们的同胞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! It's you that's betrayed our kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费我们的未来 就为了让你自己能够活在过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Squandering our future so you can cling to the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.37,0:43:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亵渎了头顶的王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You profane the crown you wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.54,0:43:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家徽放下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.95,0:43:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正再也不是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not yours anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.91,0:44:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个秋日 他捕食蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while he was a snailin' Upon that autumn day
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.62,0:44:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他任由宝宝哭泣 溪流将女儿冲走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His babe he left a-wailin' The stream took her away
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.50,0:44:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比 你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Poppy? -What are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.79,0:44:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拎个桶 你觉得我能在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fetchin' a pail, what's it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.83,0:44:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个饕餮 别吃了  这些食物我们得留着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the vittles. Stop eatin'! We have to save those.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.83,0:44:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先出去看一眼 然后我们再聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you take a look outside, and then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.29,0:44:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看看那个 哇  -我们可以把那些作物卖到市场…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that! Oh, wow! We'll go to market with that crop, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.45,0:44:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.62,0:44:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.83,0:44:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.70,0:45:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他搞定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.00,0:45:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 你敢信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you believe it, Nori?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.87,0:45:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些吃的足够我们今晚大快朵颐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's enough bounty here to feast tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.29,0:45:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剩下的足够我们撑到 迁徙到冻鱼区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and still have enough left over to last to Frozen Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.29,0:45:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔娃说她要做一种 叫“苹果香肠”的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Malva's sayin' she gonna make somethin' called apple-sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.50,0:45:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是苹果酱 -我就是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Applesauce. -That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.12,0:45:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.54,0:45:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 玛尔娃 你姐姐去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Malva. Where's your sister gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.91,0:45:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来弄 里边还有空间吗  我们好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got it. Is there more space in there? We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.83,0:45:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沿河漂流 她大声啼哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...floated down it So loudly she did wail
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛙鱼之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The King of the Frog Fishies
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.50,0:45:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她变成了一只蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turned her into a snail
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.20,0:45:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老博尔格巴克 抓住了她 如此多汁 如此香甜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Bolgerbuck he caught her So juicy and so sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.08,0:45:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这是他的小女儿 但他忍不住想…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say his little daughter He could not help but...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.66,0:47:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.91,0:47:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们走错路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.79,0:47:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去那边了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.00,0:47:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.91,0:48:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.41,0:48:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别碰她  -听见没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Leave her alone! -You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.41,0:48:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-滚开  -走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Off with you now! -Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.37,0:48:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢碰她一根毛 我就敲碎你们的脑袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You harm a hair on her foot, and I'll brain the lot of ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.95,0:49:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 好了 把手伸出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. All right. Keep your hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.20,0:49:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在把双手合起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.83,0:49:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.41,0:49:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.04,0:49:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.12,0:50:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得回家 听到我说的话了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going home. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.58,0:50:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我们一起回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.50,0:50:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.50,0:50:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-求你了 -它不会听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Please. -He won't listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.00,0:50:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不听我们任何人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't listen to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.08,0:50:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初就不应该把那个精灵拉上船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have pulled the Elf on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.45,0:51:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海里遇到她时 我就应该把她留在海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've left her in the sea, where I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.12,0:52:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.83,0:53:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄政女王在这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen Regent. Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.91,0:53:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备工作基本完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preparations are nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.04,0:53:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以在一小时内出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can depart within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.45,0:53:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中洲南方的人怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What of the Southlanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.62,0:53:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一支驻军将垫后 负责护送他们前往安全的定居点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One garrison will remain behind to escort them to a safe settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.54,0:54:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便寻找我们失踪的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And search for our missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.33,0:54:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.91,0:54:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努门诺尔不允许下跪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one kneels in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.79,0:54:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are not in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.91,0:54:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不在努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither of you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.62,0:54:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fault that is mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.58,0:54:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船只都在待命 女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our ships are waiting, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.95,0:54:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这片大陆吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us put this land behind our sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.91,0:55:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怜悯我 精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not spend your pity on me, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.16,0:55:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着将来可怜我们的敌人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save it for our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.04,0:55:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为敌人不知道它们已经挑起了大战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For they do not know what they have begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.12,0:55:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我 弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For I, Míriel,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.91,0:55:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尔帕蓝提尔之女 我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}daughter of Ar-Inzilad?n, vow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努门诺尔必将回归\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Númenor will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.54,0:55:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵将时刻准备着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Elves will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.20,0:55:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 我们随时可以出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain, we sail with the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.87,0:56:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.37,0:56:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.16,0:56:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来吧 姑娘 能拿什么就帮我拿着点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your feet now, girl. Stand up. Help me gather what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.95,0:56:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.04,0:56:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别垂头丧气的 一切都会好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let this splinter your spirit, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.08,0:56:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉哥 别骗她 她这么大了 能听得出真话假话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't lie to her, Largo. She's too old for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.91,0:56:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没撒谎 一切都会变好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't lyin'. It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.37,0:56:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 白兰地足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pity's sake, Brandyfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.25,0:56:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们哭一会儿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give us a moment to weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.12,0:56:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weepin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.87,0:56:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得我们只能哭了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that all you think we have left in us?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.45,0:56:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是毛脚族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're Harfoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.50,0:57:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会屠龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we don't slay dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.95,0:57:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对挖宝藏也没什么兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not much for diggin' jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.12,0:57:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我保证有件事我们很擅长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's one thing we can do, I warrant,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.41,0:57:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比中洲的任何生物都要做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}better than any creature in all Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.75,0:57:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们彼此忠贞不渝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We stay true to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.37,0:57:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论前路如何曲折 或多么陡峭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how the path winds, or how steep it gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.16,0:57:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们敢于直面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we face it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.83,0:57:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气和意志比我们的大脚还要强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with our hearts even bigger than our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.50,0:57:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只管继续前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we just keep walkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.87,0:58:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori. Where are you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.50,0:58:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去帮助我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To help my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.87,0:58:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告他将要发生的事情 这起码是他理应得到的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warn him what's comin'. He deserves at least that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.95,0:58:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要偏离路线 独自前往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goin' off-trail? Now? Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.29,0:58:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会独行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.75,0:58:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经抛下了许多同胞 不能把他也丢下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've left enough folk behind, we're not leavin' him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.20,0:58:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩姑娘哪儿也不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You girls aren't goin' anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.79,0:58:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须有我同去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.00,0:58:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈尔迪 你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure about this, Goldie?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.91,0:58:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们走进那片树林 可能永远都无法活着走出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go into those woods, you might never come out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.83,0:58:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有探路者一起去 她们有可能会安全返回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They might if a trail-finder were to go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.37,0:58:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白兰地足小姑娘 帮他是对的 自始至终都是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot girl was right to help him. Was right all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.45,0:59:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得玛尔娃密都格拉斯 太过骄傲而不敢承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you think Malva Meadowgrass is too proud to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.04,0:59:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨道克 那你觉得 不讲情义地活着还有什么意义吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, what's the good of livin', Sadoc, if we aren't livin' good?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.91,0:59:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 玛尔娃 哪怕就一回…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Malva, just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.20,0:59:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能承认自己不是每次都对 那可就太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, it would be grand if you weren't right all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.04,0:59:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿口粮 给我拿根拐杖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll fetch provisions and get me stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.29,0:59:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm comin' with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.12,0:59:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 反正我们终有一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter anyway, we're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.00,0:59:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 不然一整天都得待在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, otherwise we'll be here all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.75,0:59:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们能找到他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think we'll be able to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.75,0:59:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是个巨人啊 我们怎么会找不到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a bloody giant. How could we miss him?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.75,1:00:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信她会信守诺言吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You believe she'll keep her promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.37,1:00:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.58,1:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.79,1:00:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头已经固定 伤口已经包扎 我们可以出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bones have been set, wounds bound. We can travel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.79,1:00:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.79,1:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安都因河口 一个古老的努门诺尔殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An old Númenórean colony by the mouth of the Anduin.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.62,1:00:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们称之为佩拉基尔 据说那里有新鲜的水源和土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pelargir, they called it. They say there's fresh land, fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.37,1:00:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个新的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.75,1:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去向至高王报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I will report to our High King.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.00,1:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直面奖惩 任由处置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To face whatever awaits me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.95,1:00:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的国王呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what of our king?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.58,1:00:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your king?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.75,1:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人通知你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has no one informed you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.79,1:00:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Informed me of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.25,1:00:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.37,1:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you had died.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.41,1:01:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是死了反而更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better for me if I had done.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.54,1:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天夜里 南方大地的人 在路上发现他伤成了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Southlanders found him on the road like this yestereve.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.66,1:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口一夜之间就腐坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wound soured overnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.75,1:01:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试着在路上给他治疗 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought to try and treat him on the road, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.87,1:01:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个伤口需要精灵族的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wound needs Elvish medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.16,1:01:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能骑马吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can he ride?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.41,1:01:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让治疗师尽可能多带一些口粮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have the healers gather what provisions they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.62,1:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.33,1:01:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来命运又要让我们“同筏”共济了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems fate has in store for us one more raft.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.58,1:01:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.37,1:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃这片土地 也不同意他们将这里烧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not abandon these lands and condemn them to burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.08,1:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不可以放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nor will you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.75,1:02:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐国王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.83,1:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐国王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.75,1:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐国王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.75,1:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐国王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king! Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.58,1:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着吧…士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it... Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.00,1:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.58,1:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐南方大地以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.29,1:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐南方大地以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the Southlands! Strength to the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.12,1:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辜负了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I failed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.95,1:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.70,1:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.45,1:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.37,1:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.83,1:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父亲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your father's.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.70,1:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他年纪大了 太多疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's grown too old, too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.54,1:04:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思维过于羸弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His mind, too feeble.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.58,1:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双眼发昏看不清现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His eyes too dim to see
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.25,1:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他把你的多少家徽扔到地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that no matter how many crests he hurls to the floor,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.95,1:04:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 这将会是你的王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one day this will be your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.04,1:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你都林四世的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin IV's.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.12,1:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你兄弟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not your brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.91,1:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是其他矮人领主的 而是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not some other Dwarf-lord's. Yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.91,1:04:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.50,1:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们气数耗尽之前 这座山和其他所有山都将归我们统治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And together, we will rule this mountain and all others before our time is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.29,1:04:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘银属于我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That mithril belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.62,1:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.37,1:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我们一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And together, one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.95,1:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同去挖掘秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are going to dig.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.83,1:05:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把秘银矿封起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seal it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.04,1:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.66,1:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉你们的太阳斗篷和头盔吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cast off your sun-cloaks and your helms.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.00,1:06:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白日的光亮再也无法灼伤你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are no longer to be burdened by the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.95,1:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地现在属于我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is our land now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.79,1:06:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is our home.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.62,1:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致敬阿达尔 南方大地之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hail Adar, Lord of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.41,1:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致敬阿达尔 南方大地之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hail Adar, Lord of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.29,1:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致敬阿达尔 南方大地之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hail Adar, Lord of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.54,1:06:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致敬阿达尔 南方大地之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hail Adar, Lord of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.16,1:06:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.95,1:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方大地这个地方已经不存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the name of a place that no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.54,1:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 那我们应该怎么称呼它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What should we call it instead, Lord-father?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.79,1:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar! Adar!
